title: [Sylvarraend Herbals]
description: Moonlight glimmers through the glaesine windows, each framed with a swath of pale yellow gauze.  The monir planked flooring is polished to a dull sheen.  Lining the walls are shelves holding bottles and flasks of all sizes, each carefully labeled with a small tag denoting its contents.
